stanford archaeology association stanford archaeology association the stanford archaeology association is a student group dedicated to archaeology due to the fact that the new interdepartmental archaeology program offers many lectures and programs and that interest in the student association has recently waned saa is not currently active if you are interested in archaeology at stanford please visit the links below to the archaeology center cultural and social anthropology anthropological sciences classics and geophysics if you are interested in reviving saa please inquire with prof john rick who has advised the group in the past students excavating the stanford mansion in the archaeology field methods course offered alternating spring quarters archaeology fieldwork at stanford and beyond course offerings and department links undergraduate fieldwork grants past saa events archaeology links
